  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Chalet Tirol enjoys a prime location close to the main Penkenbahn gondola in the very heart of vibrant <a data-udi="umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f9068cb62c4d4b2299a0ef29fd676ed5}" title="Mayrhofen">Mayrhofen</a>. The chalet has a comfortable lounge area in which to relax in after your day skiing.</p>
<p>This comfortable and homely chalet in traditional Tirolean style occupies the upper two floors of the house, above a shop and the popular ‘Café Tirol'. Run by the owners, completely separately to the chalet, it's the most amazingly convenient place for dinner on your Chalet Hosts’ night off.</p>]]></description>
